1228
01:20:50,038 --> 01:20:57,738
See, ah, the heart is dying, ah, dying

1229
01:20:57,838 --> 01:21:00,026
In the fire-breathing lava of love.

1230
01:21:00,027 --> 01:21:00,677
In the fire-breathing lava of love. Woof!

1231
01:21:00,678 --> 01:21:04,178
In the fire-breathing lava of love.

1232
01:21:04,952 --> 01:21:12,651
The twilight smells of Jamaican rum, blue and long.

1233
01:21:12,852 --> 01:21:20,152
And the city of stone still drinks and waits for news.

1234
01:21:20,384 --> 01:21:27,384
The sunset has once more painted the street with colors that are marvelous.

1235
01:21:29,494 --> 01:21:34,319
...swirling over the volcano of passions.

1236
01:21:34,354 --> 01:21:41,984
Help me, help me, help me,

1237
01:21:42,183 --> 01:21:49,483
Yellow-eyed night call.

1238
01:21:49,833 --> 01:21:57,023
See, ah, the heart perishes, ah, the heart perishes.

1239
01:21:57,123 --> 01:21:59,421
In the fiery lava of love.

