01:23:15,624 --> 01:23:17,124
Good morning, Semyon Semyonovich!

1246
01:23:23,543 --> 01:23:25,443
No, I have to go to Dubrovka immediately.

1247
01:23:25,703 --> 01:23:27,303
That's right, but not now.

1248
01:23:28,392 --> 01:23:30,142
We'll send you a car tomorrow morning,

1249
01:23:30,329 --> 01:23:31,529
