1250
01:23:31,629 --> 01:23:32,782
8 a.m. Is that convenient for you?

1251
01:23:32,828 --> 01:23:34,128
Why not today?

1252
01:23:34,476 --> 01:23:37,024
I have a favor to ask of you today.

1253
01:23:37,025 --> 01:23:38,025
