1266
01:24:03,924 --> 01:24:04,824
Gena?

1267
01:24:05,170 --> 01:24:05,970
Yes!

1268
01:24:07,655 --> 01:24:09,200
And why didn't you...

1269
01:24:09,201 --> 01:24:11,701
